{"tid":2316581,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MC Jin《魔物獵人》遭玻璃心狙擊辱華扮愛國 今跪玻璃：為我的血統感到自豪","createTime":"2020-12-08T03:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T11:49:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca3ed602c2b18fbc66f4b6e5566b1fe710d4ce7","tid":2316581,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:35:46.000Z","msg":"大陸網民質疑MC Jin扮「愛國」賺人民幣，MC Jin怕失去大陸市場，為保飯碗急跪玻璃。MC Jin凌晨在IG貼出自拍片，講話七情上面證明自己屬於紅色光譜「政治正確」。MC Jin刻意在影片寫上簡體及英文字幕，先指近日電影《怪物獵人》在中國上映，他扮演的角色其中一句台詞，引起極大爭議，就此事向華人fans道歉，「事情發展到今天這個程度很遺憾，雖然這句台詞的本意是積極正面的。 我覺得有必要就這個問題進行說明，因為這關係到的不是我的事業，而是我內心更為珍視的東西&mdash;&mdash;我的根。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201208/77PCRJHHLFDHHOX4UKR4XIXX5M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201208%2F77PCRJHHLFDHHOX4UKR4XIXX5M%2F&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7HwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=c29e08a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201208%2F77PCRJHHLFDHHOX4UKR4XIXX5M%2F&h=217496c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201208/77PCRJHHLFDHHOX4UKR4XIXX5M/</a>"},{"pid":"8af5e8b3e8a3a5e49161e7e58f1e639f805d1348","tid":2316581,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">收皮啦</span>"},{"pid":"98bdc574c622cfc3f16e6982561136d34537ba52","tid":2316581,"uid":86504,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:15:17.000Z","msg":"美國白人警察跪頸黑人致死案震驚全球，泰勒絲(Taylor Swift)、珍妮佛羅培茲(Jennifer Lopez)、蕾哈娜、小賈斯汀、珍妮佛安妮斯頓(Jennifer Aniston)等人齊聲抗議。曾參加《中國有嘻哈》的歐陽靖也忍不住發聲，字裡行間鏗鏘有力，最後標籤「#黑人的命也很重要」做為結尾。<br />\n<br />\n許多香港民眾在歐陽靖IG留言，盼同為香港人「同根生」的他，也能聲援譴責香港警察暴力，沒想到全遭到刪文、封鎖，最後不作回應，最後甚至關閉留言功能，此舉動更被詳細列在《維基百科》中。讓許多香港網友紛紛諷刺，「MC Jina」、「中國有嘻哈，香港沒人權」、「黑人就是人，香港人不是？」"},{"pid":"3ed34965b9caba9f197baf9c42d1a563b9999c9f","tid":2316581,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:24:52.000Z","msg":"當年連登仔係咁吹佢上神台"},{"pid":"6b143d65cec24b558a2c166c4159d58108fd913d","tid":2316581,"uid":312598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"甘自豪做乜扮唔識講中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12b56f4c4e74d32e3d9bd45ea83a8db6b2a3755","tid":2316581,"uid":201197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JaAFZZs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaAFZZs.png&h=9666f15e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}